channel.title: Error when logging into 508 server
channel.description:
I've got a 508 server up and running finally(much trouble with the cache) but now I come to the logging in. I type in a name and password and hit "log in". It says "preforming login" and it either says "error connecting to server" or "Connection timed out please use a different world"
My source is Rubik's Scape with josh's 508 Ip changer client. I get no error from the clients cmd box.
Something that interests me is when I look at the servers cmd box I only see the client connecting and nothing about a person logging in
